FilterEditor - Class in net.coderazzi.filters.gui.editor
Custom component to handle the filter' editors
It includes: A editor component, usually a text field to enter the filter text. A popup menu containing both history and predefined option elements. An arrow button to display the popup menu. The component keeps the same look and feel under all cases (being editable or not, having custom cell renderers or not).
